## Tech Stack

### Backend

- Python 3.12
- Django 6
- SQLite (development)
- PostgreSQL (planned/production)

### Frontend

- HTMX
- Tailwind CSS

### Development Tools

- Docker
- Git
- GitHub
- Django Debug Toolbar

### Testing

- Django Test Framework

